Description:
DESIGN
Due to the on going success of our original marble cases we have decided to expand our range with more marble, in more colours, with more beautiful effects.
Our Marble white/grey cases are modeled off our original Marble cases and feature the same design but with a Higher level of protection for your iPhone and a high gloss finish, as opposed to the original marble cases which have a matte finish.
CONSTRUCTION
This case is constructed of heavy duty silicone/gel material and provides your device with total coverage on the back, sides, top and bottom. This case covers all the way up to the front display of your iPhone, making for a strong, durable, yet elegant and modern case that looks amazing and gives you peace of mind in protecting your device.
MORE CASES

Welcome to Supply Square where conceptual designs and protective cases combine to create individual and creative
pieces for your device.
We strive to always bring our customers beautiful and creative cases which are highly protective, fashionable, and represent your individual style. Our cases come in many shapes and sizes, using various materials such as soft TPU, Silicone and hard plastic, to not only protect your device but to offer a great finish and a matching style for your tastes.
We always use the highest quality methods in printing and production to ensure longevity of our products and to give our customers the 
best value for money.
SHIPPING
All cases are sent via standard Airmail in a bubble lined mailing bag to ensure safety in transit. For international shipping, orders generally take between 1 - 4 weeks to arrive to our customers.
For those who would like piece of mind in transit, we have added options for tracked and registered post. This gives you the ability to track the whereabouts of your order at all times and gives a more direct arrival time. For more shipping information simply click the link below.
RETURNS AND REFUNDS
As a store, we always strive to provide the most comprehensive and efficient service to our customers to ensure a great experience and great products. If you accidentally order the wrong size case you are more than welcome to return in to us in original condition for a replacement or a refund (it is our customers responsibility to cover return shipping fee back to us). If you would like to return your case please be sure to contact us prior to sending it back.
We understand that sometimes when travelling the world, our products can be damaged on arrival :( If this occurs simply contact us Immediately with a supplied photo of the condition and we will offer you a suitable solution.
CONTACT US
If you have any questions or inquires please feel free to contact us anytime and we will do our best to respond as
fast as possible.
Thanks for stopping by and happy Shopping :)
